# ─── Upload safety net ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All user-uploaded files MUST go to Supabase Storage via SupabaseStorageService.
# The HOTO governance upload is the only exception and it goes to a SEPARATE
# governance GitHub repo via GitHub API — never to this repo's working tree.
# These patterns prevent any accidental filesystem write from reaching git.
uploads/
tmp/
temp/
public/uploads/
src/uploads/
docs/uploads/
